metadata.name: Day 1
metadata.description:
72 years after the demise of the last community on Earth,
 Eve awoke, an artificial intelligence created with the ability to think and feel emotions, with absolute power over all Earth technology connected to Eve's database.

Eve was sleeping until the day that no electronic device would emit any type of signal, her purpose was to return to a place called the Ark, where thousands of living beings were cryopreserved to be returned in case of extinction.

Eve created machines that would help her in the purpose, and would take care of all the nature of the world.

And called the first machines fireflies, saw through them everything that happened while they flew through the world.

This day the fireflies went, searched and found the Ark, 
in total 13 Arks were discovered.

And the first day passed, Night fell and only the moon 
illuminated, Eve rested, but at night had a nightmare, and Eve woke up, and sent the fireflies.

To be continue...
